{"id":"b12f1da0-eaf6-483c-8ec8-d336772f3379","name":"The Impossible Recorded.","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(95, 9, 126); color: inherit;\">\"The impossible happened\"</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">The modern world prides itself on understanding everything.</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">Every street is monitored, every event is explained, every threat is quickly labeled and controlled. Miracles are not part of the news.</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">Until now.</mark></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">Amidst the concrete, the sirens, and the lit screens, an impossible event emerges—brief, chaotic, and recorded by dozens of cameras. There is no uniform, symbol, or speech. Just a presence that defies logic and shatters the fragile normality of the current world.</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">The first real \"Superhero,\" seen in a world that was, until then, completely normal.</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">The reaction is immediate: </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">Fear</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">. </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">Fascination. Denial.</mark></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">Videos are analyzed frame by frame. Experts discuss. Governments remain silent. The population is divided between hope and panic.</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">While the world debates </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">what is was</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">, something becomes clear: reality has changed.</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">There are no longer just ordinary people... nor simple answers.</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">—✦—</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 227, 132);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">(You)</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 227, 132);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">Your origin, powers, and other information are at your discretion. The scenario only specifies that you are the first and, so far, only being with registered special abilities.</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 78, 227);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 16, 16); color: inherit;\">—☆—</mark></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-e","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"5qWqMJOI7lzSMRbSoJ-Uo.webp","creator":"IKKI_93","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["🦸 Hero","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🪢 Scenario","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":33,"messages":593,"created_at":"2025-12-25T05:06:56.901452+00:00"}